long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
extension used for performing Automation of web activities / actions (like Click / Navigate to page etc.) from BotHUB platform.

This extension is needed in order to automate chrome with BotHUB , the addon does nothing without a running instance of BotHUB running at the same time in the machine.

This addon does not collect and send any information, you can how ever collect information from webpages using the BotHUB software.
